{"tid":907812,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"王嘉爾微博轉貼中國，一點都不能少","createTime":"2018-11-19T06:12:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T16:13:47.000Z","uid":74065,"like":7,"dislike":82,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"29ac1a40130f90415d57307fa6e1ea66053d03df","tid":907812,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:12:37.000Z","msg":"第55屆金馬獎，最佳紀錄片由《我們的青春，在台灣》拿下，導演傅榆上台領獎，發表得獎感言時，說：「希望我們的國家可以被當成一個真正獨立的個體來看待，這是我身為一個台灣人最大的願望」，讓中國網友生氣了。<br />\n<br />\n中國網友得知傅榆的得獎感言後，紛紛在《微博》發文指出，「台灣永遠是中國的一部分」、「台獨滾蛋」、「這麼囂張的嗎」、「她的得獎感言明天騰訊播的時候八成會被剪掉」、「李安都不敢鼓掌了」、「這位導演生涯可以結束了」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGOT7的香港成員王嘉爾也在第一時間轉發中國一點都不能少的圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WOU8xIy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FWOU8xIy.jpg&h=50fdb785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嘉爾真係香港人既偶像 6666666666666666666666666666<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1481b6b18b8a7e39e1f0c891c4f30b79134f25ba","tid":907812,"uid":1713,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:13:38.000Z","msg":"666666"},{"pid":"d45ea22c5085cc199401cdb3970e9648f1a1c780","tid":907812,"uid":14739,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:14:53.000Z","msg":"royal 級留言"},{"pid":"89c4d23100522d43f51d0205f25a986677f2a580","tid":907812,"uid":120210,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:15:42.000Z","msg":"我建議佢可以放棄香港護照"},{"pid":"1ae98a99138aa2b2477bca4a9b10c04a29ba0e3c","tid":907812,"uid":10903,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:16:17.000Z","msg":"邊撚個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91dd79f052dee6b8e7489d3ef5e613f8c